1
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,105
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Ladies and gentlemen</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,129 --> 00:00:07,379
<Default><b>we will now begin the match
between Rishia Ivyred...</b></Default>

3
00:00:07,589 --> 00:00:10,429
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I needn't worry.
Everyone wants my help.</b></Default>

4
00:00:10,679 --> 00:00:12,399
<Default><b>Everyone believes in me.</b></Default>

5
00:00:13,929 --> 00:00:15,405
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
and the unstoppable</b></Default>

6
00:00:15,429 --> 00:00:17,109
<Default><b>Perfect Hidden Justice!</b></Default>

7
00:00:17,179 --> 00:00:19,100
<Default><b>Who will emerge
victorious?</b></Default>

8
00:00:19,769 --> 00:00:21,666
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I have to win that money</b></Default>

9
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:23,450
<Default><b>so I can save
the slaves.</b></Default>

10
00:00:23,609 --> 00:00:24,929
<Default><b>Save everyone.</b></Default>

11
00:00:25,149 --> 00:00:28,820
<Default><b>I need them to understand
that I'm the one in the right!</b></Default>

12
00:00:29,699 --> 00:00:31,949
<Default><b>That I'm not inferior
to anyone else.</b></Default>

13
00:00:32,490 --> 00:00:33,850
<Default><b>I'll show them.</b></Default>

14
00:00:34,369 --> 00:00:36,209
<Default><b>I'm on the
side of justice.</b></Default>

15
00:00:36,539 --> 00:00:38,139
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir, Itsuki!</b></Default>

16
00:00:40,670 --> 00:00:44,090
<Default><b>I see. Are you
my opponent today, Rishia?</b></Default>

17
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:46,396
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
If so this will be easy.</b></Default>

18
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:47,580
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki</b></Default>

19
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:50,509
<Default><b>you saved me from a despair
I can't put into words.</b></Default>

20
00:00:51,509 --> 00:00:53,985
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Is that what you
came here to tell me?</b></Default>

21
00:00:54,009 --> 00:00:55,449
<Default><b>And so this time.</b></Default>

22
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,929
<Default><b>- [sword schwing]
- Gah!</b></Default>

23
00:00:58,179 --> 00:01:00,560
<Default><b>It's my turn to save you</b></Default>

24
00:01:01,020 --> 00:01:03,455
<Default><b>Did you just say
you're going to "save me?"</b></Default>

25
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:05,480
<Default><b>That has to be
some kinda joke.</b></Default>

26
00:01:05,650 --> 00:01:08,130
<Default><b>[KEEL] You're gonna eat
those words, Mister!</b></Default>

27
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:10,215
<Default><b>Rishia is gonna
kick your butt!</b></Default>

28
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,835
<Default><b>That's right,
she'll show you!</b></Default>

29
00:01:11,859 --> 00:01:13,965
<Default><b>[ALL] Don't let
this guy beat you, Rishia!</b></Default>

30
00:01:13,989 --> 00:01:15,465
<Default><b>[KEEL]
You can do it!</b></Default>

31
00:01:15,489 --> 00:01:17,909
<Default><b>- [cheering]
- [indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

32
00:01:21,329 --> 00:01:22,579
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

33
00:01:23,670 --> 00:01:25,270
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Now I get it.</b></Default>

34
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:27,760
<Default><b>This whole fight
was a setup, wasn't it?</b></Default>

35
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:30,195
<Default><b>You lied to me.
You tricked me</b></Default>

36
00:01:30,219 --> 00:01:32,379
<Default><b>just like you do
with everyone else!</b></Default>

37
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:35,510
<Default><b>I see now why fate
brought me here!</b></Default>

38
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,639
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

39
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,720
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

40
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:42,099
<Default><b>It's time I show the world
how evil you really are.</b></Default>

41
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,376
<Default><b>And as an instrument
of justice...</b></Default>

42
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,280
<Default><b>I'll bring you
to the truth!</b></Default>

43
00:01:46,769 --> 00:01:48,506
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki,
don't do this!</b></Default>

44
00:01:48,530 --> 00:01:50,006
<Default><b>The hell is
wrong with you?</b></Default>

45
00:01:50,030 --> 00:01:51,465
<Default><b>What does shooting
at harmless children</b></Default>

46
00:01:51,489 --> 00:01:53,729
<Default><b>have to do
with this justice of yours?</b></Default>

47
00:01:54,530 --> 00:01:55,890
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I'm...</b></Default>

48
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:58,239
<Default><b>I'm punishing
an unforgiveable evil!</b></Default>

49
00:01:58,489 --> 00:01:59,569
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

50
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,290
<Default><b>Please stop.</b></Default>

51
00:03:39,509 --> 00:03:40,759
<Default><b>[Keel gasps]</b></Default>

52
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:44,770
<Default><b>Dammit,
Itsuki, you fool.</b></Default>

53
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:50,400
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki, I'm begging you
to listen to me!</b></Default>

54
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,165
<Default><b>The Phoenix
will be reviving soon</b></Default>

55
00:03:52,189 --> 00:03:53,665
<Default><b>so you're in
danger, too!</b></Default>

56
00:03:53,689 --> 00:03:54,769
<Default><b>Naofumi!</b></Default>

57
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,580
<Default><b>Rumor has it that you've been
buying up child slaves.</b></Default>

58
00:03:58,699 --> 00:04:00,466
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Forcing them to do heavy labor</b></Default>

59
00:04:00,490 --> 00:04:03,265
<Default><b>and then keeping all the money
that they earn for yourself!</b></Default>

60
00:04:03,289 --> 00:04:04,609
<Default><b>- Huh?!
- Huh?!</b></Default>

61
00:04:04,949 --> 00:04:07,436
<Default><b>I even heard you gave
rare medicine to a slave</b></Default>

62
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,895
<Default><b>to help his sick sister</b></Default>

63
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:11,359
<Default><b>just so that you could
exploit him forever!</b></Default>

64
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:13,476
<Default><b>And even now
you're using them</b></Default>

65
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,840
<Default><b>as human shields
to protect yourself!</b></Default>

66
00:04:16,009 --> 00:04:17,509
<Default><b>You filthy coward!</b></Default>

67
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,605
<Default><b>That's not
even the worst!</b></Default>

68
00:04:19,629 --> 00:04:21,026
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
A mother came to me and said</b></Default>

69
00:04:21,050 --> 00:04:23,389
<Default><b>that the life of her son
depended on you</b></Default>

70
00:04:23,509 --> 00:04:25,995
<Default><b>but no matter how much
she begged and pleased</b></Default>

71
00:04:26,019 --> 00:04:27,656
<Default><b>you refused to help her!</b></Default>

72
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,245
<Default><b>You forgot the part
where her son was already dead.</b></Default>

73
00:04:30,269 --> 00:04:33,149
<Default><b>Why didn't you use your
miraculous powers to save him?</b></Default>

74
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,120
<Default><b>That's just
unforgivable!</b></Default>

75
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:38,110
<Default><b>[sighs] I shouldn't have
to explain this to you</b></Default>

76
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,466
<Default><b>but even a
shield like this</b></Default>

77
00:04:39,490 --> 00:04:41,490
<Default><b>can't bring people
back to life.</b></Default>

78
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:43,255
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You have some nerve
standing there</b></Default>

79
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:46,079
<Default><b>and making me out to be
the worst person imaginable.</b></Default>

80
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:49,055
<Default><b>Especially after you failed
to defeat the Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

81
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:51,559
<Default><b>which cost the lives
of countless innocents.</b></Default>

82
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,726
<Default><b>Or does it not count
when you're the one</b></Default>

83
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:55,026
<Default><b>who's responsible?</b></Default>

84
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:56,300
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

85
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:59,315
<Default><b>Changing the subject
won't help you avoid punishment</b></Default>

86
00:04:59,339 --> 00:05:01,379
<Default><b>for all of the evils
you've done.</b></Default>

87
00:05:01,589 --> 00:05:02,909
<Default><b>[Itsuki sighs]</b></Default>

88
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:05,210
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
This is a waste of my time.</b></Default>

89
00:05:05,850 --> 00:05:08,850
<Default><b>If you have no intention
of repenting for your sins.</b></Default>

90
00:05:10,019 --> 00:05:12,350
<Default><b>Then I won't show you
any mercy!</b></Default>

91
00:05:13,019 --> 00:05:14,519
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

92
00:05:16,730 --> 00:05:18,170
<Default><b>That power again?</b></Default>

93
00:05:18,779 --> 00:05:21,579
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Allow me to introduce
you to my new weapon.</b></Default>

94
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:23,240
<Default><b>The Justice Bow!</b></Default>

95
00:05:23,569 --> 00:05:25,886
<Default><b>With the full power
of this unlocked bow.</b></Default>

96
00:05:25,910 --> 00:05:28,160
<Default><b>I'll show you just
how evil you are!</b></Default>

97
00:05:28,579 --> 00:05:30,179
<Default><b>Prepare to be judged!</b></Default>

98
00:05:30,209 --> 00:05:32,620
<Default><b>[gasps]
Stop, Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

99
00:05:33,129 --> 00:05:36,500
<Default><b>Now, you'll see for yourself
just how right I am!</b></Default>

100
00:05:37,589 --> 00:05:39,089
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

101
00:05:40,970 --> 00:05:42,930
<Default><b>[grunts]
Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

102
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:49,260
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

103
00:05:53,149 --> 00:05:55,029
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
A-Are you all right?</b></Default>

104
00:05:56,149 --> 00:05:58,319
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

105
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,319
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

106
00:06:03,410 --> 00:06:05,029
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

107
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:06,490
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

108
00:06:06,579 --> 00:06:09,016
<Default><b>As the referee for this
underground coliseum</b></Default>

109
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,870
<Default><b>I must confess I was secretly
aiding the Shield Hero</b></Default>

110
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:14,170
<Default><b>behind closed doors
this whole time!</b></Default>

111
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,805
<Default><b>How forthcoming.</b></Default>

112
00:06:15,829 --> 00:06:18,549
<Default><b>If you change your ways
then you will be forgiven.</b></Default>

113
00:06:18,589 --> 00:06:20,920
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Oh, thank you</b></Default>

114
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,855
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
This power</b></Default>

115
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:25,399
<Default><b>is Itsuki being affected
by the Curse series?</b></Default>

116
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,600
<Default><b>That weapon</b></Default>

117
00:06:28,139 --> 00:06:30,139
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
It's amazing, isn't it?</b></Default>

118
00:06:30,269 --> 00:06:32,495
<Default><b>It's a bow that's been infused
with holy power</b></Default>

119
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,980
<Default><b>and given to me
by Princess Malty herself.</b></Default>

120
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,706
<Default><b>With this, I
have the power</b></Default>

121
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:38,850
<Default><b>to make the ignorant
understand me.</b></Default>

122
00:06:39,110 --> 00:06:41,870
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Now I can put them
on the path of justice!</b></Default>

123
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,675
<Default><b>Looks like
we're too late.</b></Default>

124
00:06:43,699 --> 00:06:45,925
<Default><b>I think losing to
the Spirit Tortoise broke him</b></Default>

125
00:06:45,949 --> 00:06:47,846
<Default><b>and then Bitch
got into his head.</b></Default>

126
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,596
<Default><b>The arena isn't
safe anymore.</b></Default>

127
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:51,596
<Default><b>I need you to get
everyone out of here.</b></Default>

128
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:54,620
<Default><b>Got it.
Hey, guys, everyone follow me!</b></Default>

129
00:06:56,209 --> 00:06:57,685
<Default><b>- [SADEENA] Mm.
- [S'YNE] Mm.</b></Default>

130
00:06:57,709 --> 00:06:59,879
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Come on children</b></Default>

131
00:07:01,209 --> 00:07:02,809
<Default><b>I'll take you all on!</b></Default>

132
00:07:03,009 --> 00:07:04,156
<Default><b>Once you fight me</b></Default>

133
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:06,365
<Default><b>you'll finally understand
who's truly in the right!</b></Default>

134
00:07:06,389 --> 00:07:08,406
<Default><b>[IMAGINARY CROWD (5M)]
Perfect Hidden Justice!</b></Default>

135
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:10,060
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

136
00:07:10,139 --> 00:07:11,560
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

137
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,786
<Default><b>Yeah, well I think
you're full of shit.</b></Default>

138
00:07:13,810 --> 00:07:15,495
<Default><b>Your new bow hasn't got
a damn thing</b></Default>

139
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,576
<Default><b>to do with justice.</b></Default>

140
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,125
<Default><b>It just brainwashes
people!</b></Default>

141
00:07:18,149 --> 00:07:19,245
<Default><b>That's not true!</b></Default>

142
00:07:19,269 --> 00:07:21,469
<Default><b>This bow is an instrument
of justice!</b></Default>

143
00:07:21,779 --> 00:07:24,019
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Yes.
And justice means power!</b></Default>

144
00:07:24,069 --> 00:07:26,029
<Default><b>It means proving
you're right!</b></Default>

145
00:07:26,069 --> 00:07:28,870
<Default><b>Lending aid to the weak
and humbling the strong!</b></Default>

146
00:07:29,569 --> 00:07:32,579
<Default><b>And as a Hero of Justice
I have but one job to do.</b></Default>

147
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:35,579
<Default><b>To destroy every evil
that plagues this world!</b></Default>

148
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,400
<Default><b>He's lost it.</b></Default>

149
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:39,350
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

150
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,709
<Default><b>I refuse to accept
your twisted justice!</b></Default>

151
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:50,100
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I'd almost forgotten
you were here, Rishia.</b></Default>

152
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:53,380
<Default><b>Ever since the day
I met you Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

153
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:56,480
<Default><b>I've been asking myself</b></Default>

154
00:07:57,939 --> 00:08:00,036
<Default><b>[RISHIA] I wanted more
than anything to be someone</b></Default>

155
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,745
<Default><b>who could save
those in need</b></Default>

156
00:08:01,769 --> 00:08:03,889
<Default><b>the same way
you saved me that day.</b></Default>

157
00:08:04,149 --> 00:08:06,399
<Default><b>I wanted to follow
in your footsteps!</b></Default>

158
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:10,080
<Default><b>But you're not the same person
you were back then.</b></Default>

159
00:08:10,699 --> 00:08:13,139
<Default><b>The justice I learned
from you, Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

160
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,709
<Default><b>The justice I know</b></Default>

161
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,596
<Default><b>[scoffs]
You leave me no choice.</b></Default>

162
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:22,670
<Default><b>I'll prove my actions are just
and save you once again</b></Default>

163
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:25,105
<Default><b>'Cause no matter
what anyone says</b></Default>

164
00:08:25,129 --> 00:08:27,259
<Default><b>I stand on the
side of justice!</b></Default>

165
00:08:27,629 --> 00:08:29,349
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
Muso Activation!</b></Default>

166
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:31,850
<Default><b>Hengen Muso Swordcraft.</b></Default>

167
00:08:31,930 --> 00:08:33,679
<Default><b>Shining Arrow!</b></Default>

168
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,679
<Default><b>Spiral Rush!</b></Default>

169
00:08:35,889 --> 00:08:36,980
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

170
00:08:37,350 --> 00:08:38,430
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

171
00:08:42,149 --> 00:08:44,519
<Default><b>Hengen Muso
Thrusting Swordcraft!</b></Default>

172
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,760
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Circle!</b></Default>

173
00:08:47,529 --> 00:08:48,529
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

174
00:08:49,029 --> 00:08:50,336
<Default><b>So that's how it is.</b></Default>

175
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,120
<Default><b>I guess you have gotten
a little tougher after all.</b></Default>

176
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,966
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Which makes it
all the more important</b></Default>

177
00:08:54,990 --> 00:08:57,510
<Default><b>that you understand me
and awaken to justice!</b></Default>

178
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,096
<Default><b>- [ITSUKI] If you do...
- [RISHIA] No!</b></Default>

179
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,806
<Default><b>[RISHIA] I refuse to accept
the person that you've become.</b></Default>

180
00:09:01,830 --> 00:09:04,500
<Default><b>Even if that means
I die by your hand!</b></Default>

181
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:08,630
<Default><b>Hengen Muso
Secret Technique.</b></Default>

182
00:09:08,669 --> 00:09:10,009
<Default><b>First Stance.</b></Default>

183
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:13,220
<Default><b>- Sun!
- Meteor Shot!</b></Default>

184
00:09:15,049 --> 00:09:16,369
<Default><b>Second Stance.</b></Default>

185
00:09:16,809 --> 00:09:17,929
<Default><b>Moon!</b></Default>

186
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,456
<Default><b>That shouldn't
be possible!</b></Default>

187
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,760
<Default><b>My justice can't be felled
by the weak!</b></Default>

188
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,460
<Default><b>Now, Third Stance!</b></Default>

189
00:09:24,649 --> 00:09:25,969
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Star!</b></Default>

190
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:34,409
<Default><b>That's enough! Now die!</b></Default>

191
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,620
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

192
00:09:38,909 --> 00:09:40,469
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Law Fanatic!</b></Default>

193
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,976
<Default><b>He must have boosted
his own stats!</b></Default>

194
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,145
<Default><b>Please, Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

195
00:09:48,169 --> 00:09:50,235
<Default><b>You mustn't allow that power
to corrupt you!</b></Default>

196
00:09:50,259 --> 00:09:52,196
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
You don't need it to be strong!</b></Default>

197
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,840
<Default><b>Itsuki, you idiot.</b></Default>

198
00:09:54,179 --> 00:09:55,696
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] He's so drunk
on his own justice</b></Default>

199
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,200
<Default><b>it's blinding him!</b></Default>

200
00:09:57,259 --> 00:09:59,495
<Default><b>Which means his deadly sin
must be pride!</b></Default>

201
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:01,035
<Default><b>That's enough, Itsuki!</b></Default>

202
00:10:01,059 --> 00:10:03,785
<Default><b>Keep using the Curse series
like that and you'll regret it!</b></Default>

203
00:10:03,809 --> 00:10:05,889
<Default><b>I will not be lectured
by sinners!</b></Default>

204
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,399
<Default><b>Shadow Bind,
ensnare my target!</b></Default>

205
00:10:11,529 --> 00:10:12,586
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

206
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:13,650
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

207
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,200
<Default><b>Bind Arrow!</b></Default>

208
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:18,870
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

209
00:10:19,659 --> 00:10:21,620
<Default><b>I-I'm not giving up yet!</b></Default>

210
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:23,710
<Default><b>Sorry, but this
fight is over.</b></Default>

211
00:10:24,419 --> 00:10:27,316
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I call upon thy power
and request this foolish sinner</b></Default>

212
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:28,900
<Default><b>pay for her misdeeds</b></Default>

213
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:32,129
<Default><b>by means of a fiery inferno
worthy of thy power!</b></Default>

214
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:34,485
<Default><b>May she writhe in agony</b></Default>

215
00:10:34,509 --> 00:10:36,446
<Default><b>as her dying screams
are converted</b></Default>

216
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:38,639
<Default><b>into the cries
of a raging beast!</b></Default>

217
00:10:38,889 --> 00:10:40,559
<Default><b>Bull of Phalaris!</b></Default>

218
00:10:40,929 --> 00:10:42,100
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

219
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:46,559
<Default><b>Rishia!</b></Default>

220
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:49,019
<Default><b>My victory is absolute!</b></Default>

221
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:53,029
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

222
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,310
<Default><b>Fourth Stance!</b></Default>

223
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,080
<Default><b>Demon!</b></Default>

224
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:04,580
<Default><b>My eye!</b></Default>

225
00:11:05,250 --> 00:11:08,710
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Why? Why do you have
to keep getting in my way?</b></Default>

226
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:10,566
<Default><b>I'll never forgive you!</b></Default>

227
00:11:10,590 --> 00:11:12,150
<Default><b>You don't mean that.</b></Default>

228
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:14,799
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I'll never forgive you.</b></Default>

229
00:11:15,090 --> 00:11:16,179
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

230
00:11:17,429 --> 00:11:19,179
<Default><b>I'll never forgive you.</b></Default>

231
00:11:22,059 --> 00:11:23,980
<Default><b>I'll never forgive you.</b></Default>

232
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,255
<Default><b>No, Itsuki! You
can't give in!</b></Default>

233
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,479
<Default><b>Fight back!</b></Default>

234
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:39,029
<Default><b>I will never
forgive you!</b></Default>

235
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:50,750
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Any who stand
in my way must die!</b></Default>

236
00:11:51,129 --> 00:11:54,049
<Default><b>Sir Ituski! Stop using that
power before it's too late!</b></Default>

237
00:11:54,129 --> 00:11:55,946
<Default><b>Die in the
name of justice!</b></Default>

238
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:58,549
<Default><b>This world is stained
by your evil!</b></Default>

239
00:12:06,269 --> 00:12:08,326
<Default><b>- Master Naofumi!
- Right, I'm on it!</b></Default>

240
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:10,150
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Rishia, use this!</b></Default>

241
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,880
<Default><b>I can't do that.</b></Default>

242
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:15,580
<Default><b>This battle is solely
between me and Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

243
00:12:15,690 --> 00:12:19,240
<Default><b>If I accept your weapon</b></Default>

244
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:21,340
<Default><b>Be careful, Rishia.</b></Default>

245
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,700
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

246
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,580
<Default><b>Looks like our fight
is all but finished.</b></Default>

247
00:12:25,659 --> 00:12:27,226
<Default><b>I'm just
getting started!</b></Default>

248
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,306
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Oh, really?</b></Default>

249
00:12:28,330 --> 00:12:30,186
<Default><b>And how exactly do you plan
on fighting me</b></Default>

250
00:12:30,210 --> 00:12:31,650
<Default><b>without a weapon?</b></Default>

251
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,169
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

252
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:41,439
<Default><b>Admit you're outclassed
in every way and surrender.</b></Default>

253
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,440
<Default><b>[RISHIA] No matter how much
I suffer or despair...</b></Default>

254
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:46,639
<Default><b>I will never give up!</b></Default>

255
00:12:47,059 --> 00:12:48,100
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

256
00:12:48,519 --> 00:12:50,559
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
I learned that from you.</b></Default>

257
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,375
<Default><b>That's what you taught me
when you saved me</b></Default>

258
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:54,559
<Default><b>from the depths of despair
that day.</b></Default>

259
00:12:55,230 --> 00:12:57,630
<Default><b>You taught me that justice
never gives up!</b></Default>

260
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,909
<Default><b>Don't twist my words!</b></Default>

261
00:13:00,990 --> 00:13:02,635
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Everything about you is evil!</b></Default>

262
00:13:02,659 --> 00:13:04,830
<Default><b>The opposite of justice
isn't evil!</b></Default>

263
00:13:04,950 --> 00:13:06,350
<Default><b>It's my justice!</b></Default>

264
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:09,159
<Default><b>After all, everyone holds
their own ideals</b></Default>

265
00:13:09,370 --> 00:13:10,936
<Default><b>their own
form of justice!</b></Default>

266
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,840
<Default><b>Shut up! You're a wicked stain
upon the world.</b></Default>

267
00:13:14,090 --> 00:13:15,669
<Default><b>And I am justice!</b></Default>

268
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,855
<Default><b>Using my power to rid
the world of darkness!</b></Default>

269
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:20,066
<Default><b>Then I'll fight you
with my own justice.</b></Default>

270
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:22,639
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki</b></Default>

271
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:26,139
<Default><b>Don't go spouting
your lies at me!</b></Default>

272
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:36,269
<Default><b>- What the...?
- Master Naofumi, is that...?</b></Default>

273
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:42,490
<Default><b>[ATLA]
I was able to sense it.</b></Default>

274
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:46,830
<Default><b>The evil ki
from Itsuki's bow</b></Default>

275
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,500
<Default><b>A pure ki.</b></Default>

276
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:51,620
<Default><b>The Cardinal Weapons still have
some kind of hidden power?</b></Default>

277
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:58,000
<Default><b>[gasps]
What the hell just happened?</b></Default>

278
00:13:58,379 --> 00:14:00,059
<Default><b>I see even your own bow</b></Default>

279
00:14:00,419 --> 00:14:02,970
<Default><b>rejects the perverted justice
you cling to.</b></Default>

280
00:14:03,049 --> 00:14:04,049
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

281
00:14:04,139 --> 00:14:05,865
<Default><b>Your bow gave
me this strength</b></Default>

282
00:14:05,889 --> 00:14:08,649
<Default><b>as if pleading for me to put
an end to this battle.</b></Default>

283
00:14:08,769 --> 00:14:10,559
<Default><b>That's not possible!</b></Default>

284
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:13,620
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] My bow would never
betray me like that.</b></Default>

285
00:14:13,649 --> 00:14:15,209
<Default><b>This isn't possible.</b></Default>

286
00:14:15,399 --> 00:14:18,079
<Default><b>This can't be happening.
This can't be happening!</b></Default>

287
00:14:20,399 --> 00:14:22,360
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I won't accept it!</b></Default>

288
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,200
<Default><b>Hengen Muso
Secret Throwing Technique!</b></Default>

289
00:14:30,830 --> 00:14:32,330
<Default><b>Rolling.</b></Default>

290
00:14:32,789 --> 00:14:34,169
<Default><b>Spin.</b></Default>

291
00:14:42,049 --> 00:14:43,405
<Default><b>Air Strike Throw!</b></Default>

292
00:14:43,429 --> 00:14:45,589
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
Second Throw! Dritte Throw!</b></Default>

293
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:47,929
<Default><b>Tornado Throw!</b></Default>

294
00:14:48,639 --> 00:14:50,179
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

295
00:14:50,259 --> 00:14:52,639
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

296
00:14:58,820 --> 00:14:59,860
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

297
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:11,500
<Default><b>My power.</b></Default>

298
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:14,510
<Default><b>My new power that was
supposed to save the world.</b></Default>

299
00:15:15,789 --> 00:15:19,340
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Class 3-3, Itsuki Kawasumi!</b></Default>

300
00:15:20,379 --> 00:15:21,605
<Default><b>And my dream is</b></Default>

301
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:23,985
<Default><b>to be a brave hero
who fights for what's right!</b></Default>

302
00:15:24,009 --> 00:15:26,369
<Default><b>And saves everyone
who's in need of help!</b></Default>

303
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,759
<Default><b>[applauding]</b></Default>

304
00:15:29,970 --> 00:15:32,350
<Default><b>[STUDENT 11-C]
With your power</b></Default>

305
00:15:32,929 --> 00:15:34,285
<Default><b>[STUDENT 11-B]
You're going to a middle school</b></Default>

306
00:15:34,309 --> 00:15:36,745
<Default><b>that only kids with powers
can go to, right?</b></Default>

307
00:15:36,769 --> 00:15:38,689
<Default><b>[STUDENT 11-C]
That's so cool!</b></Default>

308
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:49,580
<Default><b>[chuckles] I'm so proud
to be able to call you my son.</b></Default>

309
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:57,590
<Default><b>This can't be happening.</b></Default>

310
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,160
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I've been placed in Level E?</b></Default>

311
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,129
<Default><b>Level A's are
just amazing</b></Default>

312
00:16:04,299 --> 00:16:06,905
<Default><b>With power like yours you can
do anything you want!</b></Default>

313
00:16:06,929 --> 00:16:09,489
<Default><b>[STUDENT 11-F]
You've practically won at life!</b></Default>

314
00:16:09,850 --> 00:16:10,970
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

315
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:18,440
<Default><b>Screw this.</b></Default>

316
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:23,230
<Default><b>- [rain drumming]
- [Itsuki's mom sobbing]</b></Default>

317
00:16:32,490 --> 00:16:34,530
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I refuse to accept this.</b></Default>

318
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:38,159
<Default><b>I'm not inferior
to anyone!</b></Default>

319
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:41,119
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

320
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,980
<Default><b>[MYNE] I'm the only one
who understands you.</b></Default>

321
00:16:46,419 --> 00:16:47,696
<Default><b>[Itsuki gasps]</b></Default>

322
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,000
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

323
00:16:49,049 --> 00:16:50,946
<Default><b>I still have someone
by my side</b></Default>

324
00:16:50,970 --> 00:16:53,090
<Default><b>who chooses to believe in
who I am.</b></Default>

325
00:16:53,350 --> 00:16:54,750
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki, I...</b></Default>

326
00:16:54,929 --> 00:16:57,639
<Default><b>Princess Malty
is the only one left who...</b></Default>

327
00:16:59,809 --> 00:17:00,995
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki, wait!</b></Default>

328
00:17:01,019 --> 00:17:03,019
<Default><b>Hey, get back
here, coward!</b></Default>

329
00:17:04,109 --> 00:17:05,545
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
I'm sure Princess Malty</b></Default>

330
00:17:05,569 --> 00:17:07,409
<Default><b>will understand
everything.</b></Default>

331
00:17:07,529 --> 00:17:09,859
<Default><b>And that I'm on the side
of justice!</b></Default>

332
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:13,426
<Default><b>[MYNE] I'm the only one
who understands you.</b></Default>

333
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:16,329
<Default><b>I can tell that you care
deeply for this world</b></Default>

334
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:18,970
<Default><b>and all the innocent people
that live in it.</b></Default>

335
00:17:19,369 --> 00:17:22,209
<Default><b>[MYNE] But everyone else
only cares about themselves.</b></Default>

336
00:17:22,710 --> 00:17:25,210
<Default><b>Everyone except for you</b></Default>

337
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,606
<Default><b>No matter what
anyone says</b></Default>

338
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,946
<Default><b>you always charge ahead
to save people in need</b></Default>

339
00:17:29,970 --> 00:17:31,406
<Default><b>and stand for justice.</b></Default>

340
00:17:31,430 --> 00:17:33,235
<Default><b>The way that
every hero should.</b></Default>

341
00:17:33,259 --> 00:17:34,759
<Default><b>Yeah, but I...</b></Default>

342
00:17:35,559 --> 00:17:38,980
<Default><b>You've been
through a lot</b></Default>

343
00:17:39,230 --> 00:17:40,285
<Default><b>[Itsuki grunts]</b></Default>

344
00:17:40,309 --> 00:17:43,559
<Default><b>This is a gift for you</b></Default>

345
00:17:45,559 --> 00:17:46,730
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

346
00:17:48,529 --> 00:17:51,450
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] That's right.
I'm not the one in the wrong.</b></Default>

347
00:17:51,819 --> 00:17:53,716
<Default><b>But I need to take it
upon myself</b></Default>

348
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:55,700
<Default><b>to save the
ignorant that are.</b></Default>

349
00:17:55,910 --> 00:17:57,619
<Default><b>Because I am justice!</b></Default>

350
00:17:58,579 --> 00:17:59,939
<Default><b>I'll save them!</b></Default>

351
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:06,539
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

352
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:15,670
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

353
00:18:17,220 --> 00:18:19,340
<Default><b>Seems like Witch
left you a letter.</b></Default>

354
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:21,785
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Itsuki, you oughta read it.</b></Default>

355
00:18:21,809 --> 00:18:23,009
<Default><b>[grimacing]</b></Default>

356
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:25,859
<Default><b>All right. I'll
do it then.</b></Default>

357
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:31,940
<Default><b>If what I'm reading here
is the truth</b></Default>

358
00:18:32,029 --> 00:18:34,309
<Default><b>Bitch spent all
the prize money he won.</b></Default>

359
00:18:34,869 --> 00:18:36,069
<Default><b>[grimacing]</b></Default>

360
00:18:36,279 --> 00:18:39,579
<Default><b>[MYNE] Tell me, was it fun
pretending to be a hero?</b></Default>

361
00:18:40,039 --> 00:18:42,265
<Default><b>You looked like you were having
a grand old time</b></Default>

362
00:18:42,289 --> 00:18:44,329
<Default><b>imagining you were
saving people.</b></Default>

363
00:18:44,579 --> 00:18:47,000
<Default><b>Well, it was a lot of
easy money for us</b></Default>

364
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:49,290
<Default><b>so I really should be
thanking you.</b></Default>

365
00:18:49,339 --> 00:18:51,420
<Default><b>Oh. If you
see the Shield</b></Default>

366
00:18:51,509 --> 00:18:53,720
<Default><b>please do me a favor
and kill him.</b></Default>

367
00:18:54,089 --> 00:18:56,369
<Default><b>Do that and we'll see
each other again.</b></Default>

368
00:18:56,799 --> 00:18:57,985
<Default><b>One last thing.</b></Default>

369
00:18:58,009 --> 00:19:00,089
<Default><b>I left you another
little present.</b></Default>

370
00:19:00,259 --> 00:19:02,899
<Default><b>She says that she left him
some kind of present.</b></Default>

371
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:05,480
<Default><b>And to have fun
paying it back.</b></Default>

372
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:07,995
<Default><b>All of these
are debt notes.</b></Default>

373
00:19:08,019 --> 00:19:10,739
<Default><b>And each one of them's
marked with Itsuki's stamp.</b></Default>

374
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:12,295
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I am.</b></Default>

375
00:19:12,319 --> 00:19:13,359
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

376
00:19:14,069 --> 00:19:15,109
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

377
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:16,529
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

378
00:19:16,819 --> 00:19:17,869
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

379
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,400
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

380
00:19:22,950 --> 00:19:24,270
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I am.</b></Default>

381
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:26,119
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

382
00:19:27,329 --> 00:19:29,750
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

383
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,520
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

384
00:19:41,259 --> 00:19:43,470
<Default><b>[crows cawing]</b></Default>

385
00:19:44,430 --> 00:19:45,680
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

386
00:19:48,650 --> 00:19:50,650
<Default><b>- [Grandma 11-A laughs]
- Huh?</b></Default>

387
00:19:51,150 --> 00:19:54,279
<Default><b>[GRANDMA
11-A] Oh, Itsuki</b></Default>

388
00:19:57,319 --> 00:19:58,399
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

389
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:11,500
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

390
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:26,320
<Default><b>[RISHIA] This is Naofumi
and his party's village.</b></Default>

391
00:20:29,190 --> 00:20:31,416
<Default><b>He generously agreed
to help you pay off</b></Default>

392
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:33,280
<Default><b>all the debts
that you owe.</b></Default>

393
00:20:36,279 --> 00:20:37,795
<Default><b>And don't you worry.</b></Default>

394
00:20:37,819 --> 00:20:39,579
<Default><b>I'll be by
your side too!</b></Default>

395
00:20:39,819 --> 00:20:41,345
<Default><b>Once they're paid off</b></Default>

396
00:20:41,369 --> 00:20:43,609
<Default><b>we can go on a journey
together again!</b></Default>

397
00:20:43,990 --> 00:20:45,030
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

398
00:20:46,039 --> 00:20:47,599
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

