406
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:25,529
<Default><b>Either way, the Phoenix
will be reviving soon</b></Default>

407
00:21:25,619 --> 00:21:28,039
<Default><b>and all four heroes
are finally together</b></Default>

408
00:21:28,369 --> 00:21:30,929
<Default><b>we've even shared methods
