409
00:21:31,789 --> 00:21:34,629
<Default><b>All that's left is to make
my lands better protected.</b></Default>

410
00:21:35,670 --> 00:21:38,390
<Default><b>Do you think the Bow Hero
will eventually be okay?</b></Default>

411
00:21:39,009 --> 00:21:40,380
<Default><b>[Naofumi sighs]</b></Default>

412
00:21:40,589 --> 00:21:43,549
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] He succumbed to
the power of the Curse series.</b></Default>

413
00:21:43,849 --> 00:21:47,180
<Default><b>His companions betrayed him
and his bow rejected him.</b></Default>

414
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:53,650
<Default><b>Itsuki may have had his
